{"type":"item.completed","item":{"id":"item_47","type":"agent_message","text":"Implemented process-lifecycle observation persistence.\n\nChanged:\n\n- `cli_runner.py`: collects synchronous observations and asynchronously persists them best-effort on success and failure/timeout.\n- `factory.py` and `container.py`: threads `ObservationRepository` through all CLI runner constructors.\n- `test_runner_taxonomy.py`: adds success and timeout persistence tests.\n- No domain files changed.\n\nVerification:\n\n```text\nruff check src tests --fix\nAll checks passed!\n\nmypy src\nSuccess: no issues found in 151 source files\n\npytest -m \"not integration\" -k \"cli_runner or process_supervisor or observation or reasoner or factory\"\n55 passed, 1 skipped, 404 deselected, 1 warning\n\npytest -q\n455 passed, 5 skipped, 1 warning in 61.79s\n```\n\nGraph refreshed successfully."}}
